{"word":"ἐκκλίνω","slug":"ἐκκλίνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐϰϰλίνω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐκ\">ἐκ</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κλίνω\">κλίνω</a></el>; <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ tr.\">tr.</a> ‘bend out of the regular line’, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ intr.\">intr.</a> ‘turn away, avoid’] in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ NT\">NT</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ intr.\">intr.</a> only ‘keep away from’, <b>turn aside</b> from the path of uprightness <b><a href='B:520 3:12'>Ro 3:12</a>;</b> in the case of <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a> <b>turn away (from), avoid</b> (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> our <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ colloq.\">colloq.</a> ‘steer clear of’) <b><a href='B:520 16:17'>16:17</a>; <a href='B:670 3:11'>1 Pt 3:11</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐκκλησία\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐκκολυμβάω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}